# Scheduled jobs for django-react API
#
# Install:
#   crontab -e
#   # paste lines below (adjust paths to your machine)
#
# Or:
#   crontab api-services/backend/scripts/cron/crontab.example

# --- Transaction state machine (every minute) ---
# Expire unpaid checkouts after 15 min; complete bookings after last slot ends
* * * * * /Users/admin-2/Desktop/personal/django-react/api-services/backend/scripts/cron/process_transaction_transitions.sh

# --- CourtSlot index (daily at 01:00) ---
# Prune past slots and extend the booking horizon (default 60 days)
0 1 * * * /Users/admin-2/Desktop/personal/django-react/api-services/backend/scripts/cron/generate_court_slots.sh

# Optional: 1-year slot horizon
# 0 1 * * * /path/to/scripts/cron/generate_court_slots.sh --days 365

# Logs:
#   api-services/backend/logs/process_transaction_transitions.log
#   api-services/backend/logs/generate_court_slots.log
